OL,3,CTyne-Wear Derby: Travel advice and
OL,4,Croad closures for fans heading into
OL,5,CNewcastle
OL,7,FNewcastle and Sunderland fans have
OL,8,Fbeen urged to "play their part" in
OL,9,Fensuring the Tyne-Wear derby this
OL,10,Fweekend, on Sunday 22 March, runs
OL,11,Fsmoothly and safely.
OL,13,FNorthumbria Police, Newcastle and
OL,14,FSunderland City Councils, Nexus,
OL,15,FBritish Transport Police, the fire and
OL,16,Frescue and ambulance services say they
OL,17,Fhave coordinated a joint plan for the
OL,18,Fmatch, which will see the Magpies host
OL,19,FSunderland at St James' Park in a
OL,20,FPremier League clash.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
