OL,3,CTyne-Wear Derby: Travel advice and
OL,4,Croad closures for fans heading into
OL,5,CNewcastle
OL,7,FAs part of the plans, advice has been
OL,8,Fissued for away fans arriving into
OL,9,FNewcastle from Sunderland:
OL,11,FFurther public transport travel advice
OL,12,Fhas also been issued head of the match:
OL,14,FFor those planning to drive into
OL,15,FNewcastle city centre on Sunday, road
OL,16,Fclosures are also in place around
OL,17,FCentral Station, St James' Boulevard
OL,18,Fand Barrack Road.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
