PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1774211656
OL,3,CTyne-Wear Derby: Travel advice and
OL,4,Croad closures for fans heading into
OL,5,CNewcastle
OL,7,FThere will be a large police presence
OL,8,Fat St James' Park, police have said,
OL,9,Fto help facilitate the safe arrival
OL,10,Fand departure of all fans.
OL,12,FNorthumbria Police Chief
OL,13,FSuperintendent Mark Hall said: "We are
OL,14,Faware of and appreciate the widespread
OL,15,Fexcitement for the upcoming game
OL,16,Fbetween Newcastle United and
OL,17,FSunderland at St James' Park on Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
