PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1774211656
OL,3,CTyne-Wear Derby: Travel advice and
OL,4,Croad closures for fans heading into
OL,5,CNewcastle
OL,7,F"Football fans in our region are
OL,8,Frenowned for being among the most
OL,9,Fpassionate across the country, and the
OL,10,Freturn of this fixture has been highly
OL,11,Fanticipated among both sets of
OL,12,Fsupporters.
OL,14,F"Our role ` and that of our wider
OL,15,Fpartners ` is to help ensure that all
OL,16,Fthose in attendance are able to enjoy
OL,17,Fthe experience safely, and disruption
OL,18,Ffor other members of the public is
OL,19,Fkept to a minimum.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
